# sine_generator

A library to generate sinusoidal waveforms with a DC offset.
Usage: import sine_generator as gen
t,sine_wave=gen.sine_generate(amplitude, frequency, sampling_rate, duration)
#t: Time array
#sine_wave_with_offset: Sine wave with DC offset

## Installation

```sh
pip install sine_generator
